Name: Australian National University Library, Rare Books and Manuscripts

About.Officer in charge: Senior Librarian, Social Sciences and Humanities

About.Hours & facilities: Open Mon-Fri 9am-5pm. No reference service available. Copying services available for original records to A3.

About.Access: In some cases access can be gained by permission of donor only.

About.References: McGrath, Dermid, 'The Manuscripts Collections of the Australian National University Library' Archives and Manuscripts, 9/2 (December 1981): 28-34.
